                        SAMUEL WILSON
                  , LORD MAYOR of the City of London; Sir John Vaughan, Knt., one of the Justices of Her Majesty's Court of Common Pleas; 


                     Sir James Williams, Knt., one of the Justices of Her Majesty's Court of Queen's Bench; 


                     Anthony Brown, Esq.; Sir Peter Laurie, Knt.; 


                     Thomas Kelly, Esq.; Alder
men of the said City: the Honourable Charles Ewan Law, Recorder of the said City; Sir Chapman Marshall, Knt.; James Harmer, Esq.; John Lainson, Esq.; James White, Esq.; and Michael Gibbs, Esq.; Alder
